Vietnam has more than 37 million motorbikes and scooters . 
  The Flash Pack's Lee Thompson captured the wacky things people carry on the back of a bike or scooter in southeast Asia . 
  He was on a tour of Vietnam and Cambodia with a group of nine tourists this month . 
  In Vietnam there are more than 20 million scooters on the road . 
  The men and women of the country are known to carry livestock on their bikes . 
 